84
00:04:38,186 --> 00:04:41,728
you may even as somebody who works in community as a community professional,

85
00:04:42,228 --> 00:04:46,431
carry this reputation to other jobs that you take for other games.

86
00:04:46,851 --> 00:04:48,012
So you need to think about that.

87
00:04:48,072 --> 00:04:49,673
Now, of course, you wanna do a good job and

88
00:04:49,713 --> 00:04:51,675
be thoughtful because that's the right thing to do.

89
00:04:52,175 --> 00:04:54,416
But also, it will affect your reputation.

90
00:04:55,786 --> 00:04:57,448
They've been feeling it for a while too.

91
00:04:57,488 --> 00:04:59,972
There have probably been lots of rumors

